name: Cranberry Kush
description: Cranberry Kush is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between unknown parent strains. This strain is 30% sativa and 70% indica. Cranberry Kush is 19% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Bred by Cannabis Social Club, the average price of Cranberry Kush typically ranges from $10-$15 per gram.
